  "text": "FLI1 cDNA was subcloned into pFcDNA3.1, as previously described [CITATION_1] . MCF-10A cells stably transfected with FLI1 shRNA were transiently transfected with either FLI1 expressing pFcDNA3.1 or control pFcDNA using FuGENE HD (Roche), per manufacturer's protocol.",
